The basic syntax is:

kubectl -n namespace port-forward pod-name localPort:destPort

So for example if my name is mbell, and I've launched our friend the sample deployment

kubectl -n ws-mbell port-forward pod-name 8080:8080

Would allow you to curl http://127.0.0.1:8080/debug

on the pod.

Try also

kubectl -n ws-mbell port-forward pod-name 1234:1234

and open your web browser at http://127.0.0.1:1234

what do you see?
